items.title: Uber beats fourth-quarter revenue expectations but offers soft guidance
items.description: Uber's mobility segment reported $6.91 billion in revenue, up 25% from a year earlier. StreetAccount analysts were expecting $6.77 billion.

items.title: Disney tops quarterly profit estimates, but starts to lose Disney+ streaming subscribers
items.description: The company's streaming business reported another quarter of profitability despite a 1% decline in subscribers for Disney+.
